    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376190/extras/5206098651740f2ef43026326bbd43b5.webp?t=1714390263\" width=621 height=46 /></span><br>Welcome to Water Buddy! <br><br>The town is on fire, but no one seems to care. Good thing you're here to save the day! You'll need help from your water buddies. All you'll need to do is find them. They're hidden all over the town, wherever water is found. Find all water, by any means, and put out that fire!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376190/extras/1bd3a0964712f8180ea4361de336ac7a.poster.avif?t=1714390263\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376190/extras/1bd3a0964712f8180ea4361de336ac7a.webm?t=1714390263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376190/extras/1bd3a0964712f8180ea4361de336ac7a.mp4?t=1714390263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Cute buddies</strong><br>The goal of the game is to find all water in the game and pull your buddies out of it. Once you find all of your buddies you'll be able to put out the fire. Sometimes getting your buddies out of the water is a multi-step process where you'll have to interact with other objects first. Don't worry, your buddies will help!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376190/extras/0a8d962e96271934632e554ed8979330.poster.avif?t=1714390263\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376190/extras/0a8d962e96271934632e554ed8979330.webm?t=1714390263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376190/extras/0a8d962e96271934632e554ed8979330.mp4?t=1714390263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Oblivious townsfolk</strong><br>Those townsfolk just don't seem to notice their town is on fire, leading to a bunch of wacky encounters!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Third person exploration with light puzzles and platforming<br></li><li> Silly and memorable moments<br></li><li> A 20-30 minute experience that can be played in one sitting<br></li><li> Enjoyable for the whole family (6+ years old)</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376190/extras/5206098651740f2ef43026326bbd43b5.webp?t=1714390263\" width=621 height=46 /></span>",
